data.description: Rare opportunity! Almost 10 acres close to town. This single story home features hardwood floors throughout the entire house, primary suite with ceramic tiled walk in shower and jetted tub. Two extra bedrooms, on the opposite side of the house, have their own full bathroom. Suite opens to the private covered deck and backyard with lush pastures, huge barn, pond, orchard, & christmas trees.
